tforward — we will devote all our resources to it.</blockquote>\r\n<h1>Free Consultation</h1>\r\nYou may contact us at any time for a free consultation, with no obligations. You will speak directly to an experienced attorney. Please call us now, so we can begin helping you. Thank you for choosing the Law Offices of David Azizi.\r\n<h1>Why Clients Choose Us as Their Lawyers</h1>\r\n<strong><ul>\r\n	<li>Reputation for Large Settlements and Verdicts</li>\r\n	<li>We Specialize Exclusively in Accident and Injury Cases</li>\r\n	<li>We Advance All Costs and Expenses</li>\r\n	<li>You Pay Nothing Until We Win Your Case</li>\r\n	<li>We Fight For the Maximum Compensation</li>\r\n	<li>Experienced Trial Lawyers</li>\r\n	<li>Call Toll Free to Speak Directly with a Lawyer\r\nNO CHARGE\r\nNO OBLIGATION</li>\r\n</ul></strong>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '25-autosave', '', '', '2013-05-24 21:41:51', '2013-05-24 21:41:51', '', 25, 'http://azizipersonalinjury.com/main/?p=27', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
