INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(193, 2, '2013-04-30 07:08:00', '2013-04-30 07:08:00', '<h1>Car Accident Claims Settled by AziziPersonalInjury.com</h1>\r\nWell over six million auto accidents occur each year, and every year the number continues to rise. This appalling number includes accidents between two vehicles, those between one vehicle and someone else using the road, and those that involve one vehicle and some object. Worse, over forty thousand people lose their lives each year from car crashes, and nearly every one of these tragic deaths was preventable. \r\n\r\nOver ninety percent of these accidents involve cars or light trucks and also result in nearly three million injuries each year. When you consider the medical costs, the time and wages lost from work, recovery expenses for people and property, it''s clear that an experienced personal injury lawyer should be consulted if you or a loved one has been involved in any accident where he or she was not at fault. \r\n\r\nWhile it may not be your first instinct, having a personal injury lawyer on your side following an auto accident should be second only to quickly receiving proper and prompt medical care for anyone who was injured in the accident. While you may be in shock after an accident, you should try to avoid panicking and the following steps should be taken: \r\n\r\n1)	Determine if anyone was injured and seek professional medical assistance if it is needed. Do not attempt to move any injured persons, but mark the scene of the accident with cones and flares if possible.\r\n2)	Move the vehicles involved to the side of the road if possible, away from traffic that may add to the accident.\r\n3)	Notify the police and wait for them to arrive and conduct an accident investigation.\r\n4)	Get the names and personal information, including insurance, of everyone involved in the accident, including any witnesses or passengers.\r\n5)	In spite of the shock and adrenaline, do not discuss the accident with anyone except the police. \r\n6)	Contact a knowledgeable and experienced personal injury attorney at AziziPersonalInjury.com\r\n\r\nSoon after the accident you can expect to be contacted by insurance companies who will offer a settlement. While this settlement may be in their best interests, it is not always in yours, and you should avoid signing or accepting any proposal until you have consulted with an attorney. The amount you are offered may not cover all your expenses,expenses and one of our attorneys can make sure that you receive full compensation for every cost, now and for the future.\r\n\r\nPlease contact us for a free initial consultation, without any obligation, if you have suffered the loss of a loved one or have been injured in any accident that was not your fault. We can help you get through the maze of insurance issues and make sure that nothing is left out of your settlement, and we never charge until your case is resolved. You need a dedicated personal injury lawyer who knows all the tricks the others will use to get you to sign away your only chance to receive a settlement that''s fair for you, and we''ll make sure your interests are not among your losses.', 'Car Accidents Settled by AziziPersonalInjury.com', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '124-revision-3', '', '', '2013-04-30 07:08:00', '2013-04-30 07:08:00', '', 124, 'http://azizipersonalinjury.com/main/124-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(169, 2, '2013-04-30 06:39:12', '2013-04-30 06:39:12', '<h1>Brain Injury Lawyers in Los Angeles and California</h1>\r\nIf you or a family member has suffered from a brain injury as a result of an accident or other catastrophic event, you will need the assistance of an experienced personal injury lawyer from the Law Offices of David Azizi to handle the case. The effects of brain injuries can last for years, even decades, and you may be responsible for expensive medical bills, counseling and other health care cost. AzizPersonalInjuyr.com can help you litigate your brain injury case and ensure that you receive the appropriate compensation for damages which you deserve. \r\n\r\n<h3>Why Work with a Brain Injury Lawyer? </h3>\r\n\r\nDealing with traumatic brain injury can be a complicated process, and most health care providers do not have the resources to cover all of the recovery and rehabilitation costs involved. Victims of a brain injury, their families and/or caregivers need specialized legal representation to assist them in litigating a solid case against the offending negligent party. AziziPersonalInjury.com can help you with every stage of this process, and our lawyers have extensive experience in the field to represent your interest vigorously. \r\n\r\n<h3>What are the Symptoms of Brain Injury? </h3>\r\n\r\nMany symptoms of brain injury do not show up for several weeks or months after the initial accident or event, so it is important to recognize the symptoms as soon as they begin to interfere with day-to-day life activities. When brain functions are disrupted, the individual may experience:\r\nDisturbed sleep patterns\r\nSlowed or impaired thinking\r\nDifficulty concentrating\r\nMemory lapses\r\nFaulty judgement\r\nPeriods of depression\r\n\r\n\r\nIn many cases, the individual will need to undergo cognitive and neurological testing to find out how severe the brain injury is, and what parts of the brain have been damaged. \r\n\r\nAll of these effects and the medical care that the individual needs must be taken on by the patient or their families. This financial burden may be reduced with the help of a personal injury attorney from AzizPersonalInjury.com; our firm will do everything possible to keep the client’s best interests in mind, and do the work necessary to build a solid case. \r\n\r\n<h3>How the Law Office of David Azizi Can Assist You with your Brain Injury Case? </h3>\r\n\r\nAt AziziPersonalInjury.com, we offer a free, no obligation initial consultation. If we accept your case, we will not charge you until the case has been resolved. ', 'Brain Injury Lawyers in Los Angeles and California', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '116-revision-3', '', '', '2013-04-30 06:39:12', '2013-04-30 06:39:12', '', 116, 'http://azizipersonalinjury.com/main/116-revision-3/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
