INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(184, 2, '2013-04-30 06:57:43', '2013-04-30 06:57:43', '<h1>Quadriplegia Injury</h1>\r\nOne of the most tragic and physically devastating injuries someone can endure is a quadriplegia injury. Quadriplegia injuries can result in a lifetime of pain and discomfort as the victim loses all sensation and the ability to move their four limbs. If you or a loved one have become quadriplegic as a result of an accident or negligence, you will need the assistance of an experienced quadriplegia attorney to handle your case. The professionals at AziziPersonalInjury.com have extensive experience in representing quadriplegia cases, and can provide guidance and support when you need to file a claim or lawsuit. \r\n\r\n<h3>Common Causes of Quadriplegia </h3>\r\n\r\nQuadriplegia is also known as ‘tetraplegia’, and is the complete paralysis of all four limbs as a result of severe spinal damage. Serious cases rarely improve over time, and the victim typically needs extensive medical care and attention throughout the course of his or her life. Excessive damage to the spinal cord can be a result of several types of accidents and injuries such as:\r\nAutomobile accidents\r\nConstruction or on-the-job incidents\r\nMotorcycle or biking accidents\r\nSporting accidents\r\nDefective products\r\n\r\nThe medical expenses and rehabilitative care involved with taking care of a quadriplegic can put a financial strain on any family or victim. Working with an experienced quadriplegia lawyer from the Law Office of David Azizi means you can count on professional legal representation to recover compensation for your damages which you deserve. \r\n\r\n<h3>Working with a Quadriplegia Attorney </h3>\r\n\r\nWe have extensive experience in representing clients involved in personal injury cases and specialize in injuries related to spinal cord damage. We will do everything legally possible to aggressively pursue your case and to ensure that you and your family are not taken advantage of by insurance companies and medical providers. \r\n\r\nYou don’t have to resort to personal loans, credit cards or other financial resources just to cover the cost of medical bills; allow our quadriplegia attorneys to assess your case and assist you with receiving adequate and fair compensation for your damages. \r\n\r\nAt AziziPersonalInjury.com, we take the time to investigate your case and aggressively litigate your claim order to build a solid case against the offending party. Contact us today for a free, no obligation consultation so that we can determine the best course of action for your quadriplegia case. We will not charge you a single dollar until your case is resolved.', 'Quadriplegia Injuries', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '150-revision-2', '', '', '2013-04-30 06:57:43', '2013-04-30 06:57:43', '', 150, 'http://azizipersonalinjury.com/main/150-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(185, 2, '2013-04-30 06:58:16', '2013-04-30 06:58:16', '<h1>Azizi Personal Injury Can Handle Your Los Angeles Slip and Fall Accident Case</h1>\r\nSlip and fall accidents are common and include not only injury-causing tumbles on wet or uneven floors, but falls from scaffolds and staircases and other elevated places. Many of these accidents result in serious injury, especially to the back, and there can be costly, long-lasting effects. If the spinal cord or head is injured, the consequences can be even worse, and a personal injury lawyer dedicated to making sure your case is presented strongly can help you recover more than the insurance company is likely to offer.\r\n\r\nWhile your immediate concern after being hurt in a slip-and-fall accident should be receiving all the proper medical care to treat your injuries, you should contact us for a free consultation as soon as you can. After discussing your case, we can determine if negligence contributed to your accident and, since we work on a contingency basis, if we take your case, there is never any charge to you until the matter is fully resolved.\r\n\r\nWe have the experience and determination to fully investigate your case, and we are always willing to see it through to the end in court. The insurance company will try to get a quick settlement that only takes its own interests into account, but we know that your health and prosperity is all that matters. Instead of ignoring long-term consequences, we''ll make sure that you receive full compensation for both current and future expenses and loss of income your accident may have caused.\r\n\r\nPlease contact us today at (800) 991-LAW2 for a free consultation where your case can be discussed in privacy and without obligation or any stress. We know how to present your case in the strongest possible way, and we''ll make sure that your pain, suffering, and that all your medical and work-related needs and expenses are included in your settlement