INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(186, 2, '2013-04-30 06:59:45', '2013-04-30 06:59:45', '<h1>Spinal Cord Injury</h1>\r\nA spinal cord injury can be a physically, emotionally and financially devastating experience. Victims of a spinal injury often suffer from the side effects of the injury for years, even decades, and the financial burden of ongoing medical expenses, the inability to work, and the responsibility to pay for physical rehabilitation can be stressful. The Law Office of David Aziz can reduce the stress of handling spinal cord injuries by developing a strong case against the negligent party. We have extensive experience in personal injury law, and are dedicated to making sure you receive the full compensation you deserve. \r\n\r\n<h3>Types of Spinal Cord Injuries </h3>\r\n\r\nSpinal cord injuries typically take the form of a herniated disc in the spinal column, thoracic injuries and central cord syndrome. Most back injuries are the result of an auto accident, truck crash a construction accident where the victim’s back bones become separated or in more severe cases, broken. The most common types of spinal cord injuries include:\r\nHerniated disc injuries – also known as a bulging disc or ruptured disc, this type of spinal cord injury typically occurs when the small bone connected to the spine separates the human back bones and creates pressure on the spinal column. The effects of this type of injury include shoulder pain, leg pain and lower back pain.\r\nThoracic injuries – these injuries are sustained in the abdominal muscle area and result in paraplegia. This means the individual typically cannot move their legs or feet as a result of the violent impact to the spine.\r\nCentral cord syndrome - this is an incomplete spinal cord injury that results in the impairment of the arms and hands. The damage typically occurs in the upper regions of the spinal cord and often leads to extensive sensory loss.\r\n\r\nA spinal cord injury can be serious and even life threatening. If you were involved in an accident that caused injury to your spine, contact the Law Offices of David Azizi so that we may provide a free evaluation of your claim. \r\n\r\n<h3>Working with a Spinal Cord Injury Lawyer </h3>\r\n\r\nAziziPersonalInjury.com has extensive experience in litigating spinal cord injury cases. We can help you recover appropriate compensation for your damages which you deserve that were caused by the traumatic event. Unfortunately, many insurance companies will try to reduce the gravity of the situation and reach a quick settlement; however, this does not take your best interests into account, and you may end up paying far more out-of-pocket expenses than you should. \r\n\r\nOur firm is dedicated to making sure you receive adequate compensation for your damages related to your spinal cord injury case. We will litigate your case using all of our resources and years of expertise in the field. We will determine your actual medical condition, find out how long your injuries will cause pain and suffering, and determine what your work-related needs and expenses may be. These details will need to be included in your settlement, and you can count on us to help you every step of the way. \r\n\r\nContact us today for a free, no obligation consultation and find out how we can help you receive the full compensation you deserve from your spinal injury case.', 'Spinal Cord Injuries', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '154-revision-2', '', '', '2013-04-30 06:59:45', '2013-04-30 06:59:45', '', 154, 'http://azizipersonalinjury.com/main/154-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(187, 2, '2013-04-30 07:00:50', '2013-04-30 07:00:50', '<h1>Train Accidents</h1>\r\nIf you have been involved in a railroad crossing accident, a train crash or automobile-train collision, you will need the assistance of a train accident lawyer to represent you in your case. Train transportation continues to be one of the most popular methods of transportation and shipping, especially in Los Angeles and the surrounding community. However, California train accidents have become more common as more people turn to commuter rails and other types of trains for daily transportation. \r\n\r\nPersonal injury lawyers from AziziPersonalInjury.com have extensive experience in representing clients that have suffered from train accidents and injuries that result from a train crash. \r\n\r\n<h3>Common Causes of Train Accidents </h3>\r\n\r\nThe most common causes of train accidents include:\r\nDerailments\r\nTrain collisions with other trains\r\nTrain collisions with cars\r\nTrain collisions with pedestrians\r\nOn-board accidents\r\nMechanical failure\r\n\r\nThe accident may also be the result of several events such as driver negligence, unmarked railway crossings, poorly maintained railway equipment or driver fatigue. However, all trains are governed by State laws and you will need formal legal representation. \r\n\r\n<h3>Common Injuries Sustained from a Train Accident </h3>\r\n\r\nA personal injury lawyer can help you receive compensation for damages as a result of injuries from the accident. The most common injuries that occur from a train accident include:\r\nBrain injury\r\nSpinal cord injuries\r\nJoint or muscle pain that requres medical care/rehabilitation\r\nMigraines and headaches\r\nBurn injuries\r\n\r\n<h3>Working with a Train Accident Lawyer </h3>\r\n\r\nAn experienced train accident lawyer from AziziPersonalInjury.com will determine the scope of your case and outline all damages incurred both directly and indirectly from the accident. Train accident lawyers at AziziPersonalInjury.com will litigate your case against the negligent parties to help you receive the compensation you deserve. \r\n\r\nHigh speed train accidents can be tragic or lead to serious injuries, and you will need the assistance of a professional law firm to represent you when you pursue compensation for damages. No matter what type of accident you have been involved in, it is in your best interest to work with the experienced team of professionals at AziziPersonalInjury.com to litigate the case against the offending parties. \r\n\r\nContact the professionals at AziziPersonalInjury.com today for a free, no obligation consultation.', 'Train Accidents', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '156-revision-2', '', '', '2013-04-30 07:00:50', '2013-04-30 07:00:50', '', 156, 'http://azizipersonalinjury.com/main/156-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(188, 2, '2013-04-30 07:01:38', '2013-04-30 07:01:38', '<h1>Truck Accidents</h1>\r\nHave you or a loved one been a victim of a truck accident? Truck accidents can occur at any time and often result in serious injuries or in some cases, wrongful death. If you have been struck by a truck as a motorist or pedestrian, you may also be able to file a lawsuit or claim against the negligent truck driver. \r\n\r\nThe Law Office of David Azizi has extensive experience in representing clients involved in truck accident cases. We can help you receive appropriate compensation for your damages to cover medical expenses and other injury-related expenses incurred. \r\n\r\n<h3>When to Contact a Truck Accident Attorney </h3>\r\n\r\nContacting a truck accident attorney as soon as possible is the best course of action, because this allows the attorney to start investigating the case and gather essential details and evidence immediately after the accident. Common truck accidents include:\r\nBig rig crashes\r\nManufacturer defects in trucking equipment\r\nSemi and car collisions\r\nTractor-trailer wrecks\r\nTruck and vehicle collisions\r\nTruck and property collisions\r\nPedestrian being hit by a truck\r\n\r\n<h3>Working with a Truck Accident Lawyer </h3>\r\n\r\nThe Law Office of David Azizi has provided professional legal representation to help clients file a claim or a lawsuit against the offending party after a truck accident. We understand the extent of damages involved with serious truck accidents and have years of experience in the field of personal injury; you can count on us to help you recover appropriate compensation for your injuries. \r\n\r\nOur dedicated team is committed to helping you win your case. We will not charge you any fees for the consultation or for our services until the case is resolved. Contact us today to for a free, no obligation consultation.', 'Truck Accidents', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '158-revision-2', '', '', '2013-